wikipedia_page.main: Ashley James Corker (born 18 September 1990) is an English part-time footballer currently at Wanneroo Soccer Club. He plays as a left back.

response: On 31 January 2011 Walker and teammate Ashley Corker were released by mutual consent from the Cobblers.

He made his professional debut for the Cobblers on 8 October 2011, in a 1–0 home defeat to Crawley Town, replacing Ashley Corker in the second half. His first start for the club came a week later in a 3–0 defeat to Port Vale at Vale Park.
